column2: select t.albumid, count(*) as num,count(distinct composer) as numC from chinook.track t  group by t.albumid  ) select * from a   join chinook.track t on t.albumid=a.albumid   join chinook.album b on b.albumid=a.albumid   join chinook.artist a on a.artistid=b.artistid    where a.numC between # and #   order by
